32
00:01:16,743 --> 00:01:20,441
Shaun, you have responsibilities.
We've gotta sort this out.

33
00:01:20,514 --> 00:01:22,325
I'll give you five seconds
to get the hell out of here...

34
00:01:22,349 --> 00:01:23,726
- Shaun?
