35
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:26,151
Shaun, I just want...

36
00:01:27,754 --> 00:01:28,778
Five...

37
00:01:29,122 --> 00:01:30,181
Shaun?

38
00:01:30,624 --> 00:01:31,990
Shaun, she's calling the police.

39
00:01:32,092 --> 00:01:34,425
- Is that what you want?
- Four, three...

40
00:01:35,195 --> 00:01:36,823
- Two, one...
- Okay, okay.

41
00:01:36,930 --> 00:01:38,296
Okay, okay, I'm leaving.

42
00:01:38,966 --> 00:01:42,300
It's just that Shaun has a
tendency to run away from conflict.

43
00:01:42,536 --> 00:01:44,767
And in Casper and medical school

44
00:01:44,838 --> 00:01:47,137
people will give you a
little bit of slack, but he...

45
00:01:47,307 --> 00:01:50,709
Now he's in a very hard-to-get job
in a very competitive environment

46
