where people do not
give you a second chance.

47
00:01:54,214 --> 00:01:56,479
Still. Not cool.

48
00:02:01,455 --> 00:02:02,684
If you speak with him,

49
00:02:04,358 --> 00:02:05,958
will you call me, please?

50
00:02:06,293 --> 00:02:07,317
Out.

51
00:02:09,463 --> 00:02:10,487
Yeah.

52
00:02:23,143 --> 00:02:24,236
So, what's your plan now?

53
00:02:27,714 --> 00:02:28,841
I don't know.

54
00:02:40,594 --> 00:02:43,189
I gotta say, he seems
like a nebby old jerk.

55
00:02:43,263 --> 00:02:44,322
And a bully.

56
00:02:44,398 --> 00:02:45,764
What's "nebby"?

57
00:02:45,899 --> 00:02:48,095
Nosy. It's a Pittsburgh thing.

58
00:02:48,368 --> 00:02:50,030
I mean, you're a grown man.

59
00:02:50,103 --> 00:02:52,384
