62
00:02:58,845 --> 00:03:00,336
I'm not the biggest
fan myself, but...

63
00:03:00,414 --> 00:03:02,406
I don't wanna see a therapist.

64
00:03:03,383 --> 00:03:04,407
So, don't.

65
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:09,615
I should go back to Casper.

66
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:10,951
I have a rule.

67
00:03:11,058 --> 00:03:13,118
Never make an important decision

68
00:03:13,226 --> 00:03:18,255
while you are angry, upset, high,
or right before, or after having sex.

69
00:03:18,765 --> 00:03:20,427
Okay? You are overworked,

70
00:03:20,534 --> 00:03:22,230
stressed out and
pissed off at your boss.

71
00:03:22,436 --> 00:03:25,065
Now is not the time to
be making a big decision.

72
00:03:25,372 --> 00:03:28,467
You need to take a
break, clear your head.

73
00:03:28,608 --> 00:03:29,632
You need a vacation.

74
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:33,975
I have to work five more
months before I earn a vacation.

75
00:03:34,147 --> 00:03:35,274
So, call in sick.

76
00:03:36,149 --> 00:03:37,640
I'm not sick.

77
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:39,948
You're so adorable.

78
00:03:40,053 --> 00:03:42,750
You don't have to
be sick to call in sick.

79
00:03:43,090 --> 00:03:45,286
I have so much to
teach you, Grasshopper.

80
00:03:45,459 --> 00:03:48,486
And I'm gonna start with a
good old-fashioned road trip.

81
00:03:48,595 --> 00:03:50,325
It's the perfect way
to get your mojo back.

82
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:52,399
And when we return,
you're gonna know exactly

83
00:03:52,499 --> 00:03:56,436
what to do about San Jose,
therapy, and Glassy the Grouch.

84
00:03:56,503 --> 00:03:59,962
And all you have to do to attain
this superior wisdom and knowledge

85
00:04:00,107 --> 00:04:02,167
is to call

86
00:04:03,243 --> 00:04:05,474
in sick.

87
00:04:11,651 --> 00:04:13,244
Okay. Okay, I will.

88
00:04:16,456 --> 00:04:19,119
Dr. Melendez.
Got a case for you.

89
00:04:19,359 --> 00:04:20,987
My schedule's
pretty packed today.

90
00:04:21,094 --> 00:04:23,586
It's a patient of mine. She
needs a kidney transplant.

91
00:04:24,331 --> 00:04:25,424
You have a donor?

92
